{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>MoonFire: A Seeker\u2019s Saga</strong> is a crafted blend of a Visual Novel and an RPG-lite with Open-World segments. Set within a dark fantasy saga, you'll encounter dozens of characters within this multi-era lore. Manage six main traits inspired by tabletop RPGs with RNG dice rolls, party stats, and more, as you embark on a journey across Malenthia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover the stories Tavnorr holds, and choose to uphold your honor or live by your own rules. Manage your stats and dialogue choices, shaping your personality and the reactions of those around you. Beware, as some decisions may not only put your fate at risk, but the fate of others as well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874550/extras/s-features.png?t=1733524537\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build a roster of delightful companions  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Level your character to master in diplomacy or hone your swordplay </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect items to hoard, sell, or aid in your exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">TTRPG-Esque rolls and RNG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Freely explore a fantasy world on the brim of darkness and deceit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Story and Turn-Based combat </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique character personality system</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874550/extras/s-explore22.png?t=1733524537\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874550/extras/map-steam_gif_orig.gif?t=1733524537\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Additional adventures through side quests</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Campsites to explore and rest</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Opportunities to bond with your favorite companions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1874550/extras/s-story.png?t=1733524537\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are awake now.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I know you can't speak. You will, soon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Seeker has saved you for this quest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are in Malenthia, a land once whole and strong. The Second Era ended with the death of Queen Kulviete, many years ago. She and her family succumbed, and now the lands of Malenthia begin to crumble under the encroachment of fiends, beings of unknown origin that devour all in their path. Rumors and unrest grow into endless dispute under the spiteful gaze of one called Damaskia.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I know you have no memory of this. It must be this way. As the only human amid Creature-Kind, you must learn as you travel across Malenthia. Yours is the power of gods and demons alike, to use reason to put to rest the all-consuming chaos. Within this puzzle of scattered pieces, everything can be connected, if you can bring your mind and heart to bear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have questions. I am sure... But will you find what you seek?</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Rein Survives <3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1874550/9c69c218989880b92061e1a9859e0561fc93f12c.jpg"},{"name":"Complete Chapter 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1874550/a8769267a48d694d2c82a8c58b842b7f1f13b65e.jpg"},{"name":"Spare His Life","path":"https://cdn.akamai.s